{"tid":1419224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益 事後檢討）作為港島橪既我有野想講 麻煩入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:56:43.000Z","uid":129445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61bfbe77b8e596549b4aa4eea1af72c7999b4d35","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:28:05.000Z","msg":"由於琴日港島區太無所事事 冇人討論 得一班福建佬打過人咁大把 所以我決定首先簡單講下我角度。等大家知咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日，晏晝係金鐘本身好和平 去到3點令鐘冇啦啦射哂tg，不過大家上哂gear所以未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我人在前線 睇到大家都好淡定 好快就熄到彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（都係有人冇gear呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日中哂 點搞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n不過僵持咗一陣 開始<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇啦啦</span></span>聽到有聲音不如轉場去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />轉場？先唔講cwb呢個地方好唔好。ok 人地拎哂制高點 又唔出嚟 我地只係熄煙冇用 我明呀。咁咪轉囉 唔緊要。好快 我係前面都聽到好多人話走 都見到好多人集合物資去cwb<br />\n<br />\n去到cwb就精彩囉..一去到啱啱拎哂物資姐 又聽到有人逐個逐個講 一陣7點去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">油塘</span></span>話去塞東隧又剩 叫我地散下物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢下我開始諗唔明啦，屌你一隻狗都冇 又話走 咁一開頭嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但唔緊要！</span>我個人認為銅鑼灣都唔係好地方 一早閂哂鋪封哂路 自己本身就係死城 過去都冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽你地講 轉囉<br />\n<br />\n過多幾分鐘 去到7點啦，喂屌 冇人行既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知係d人攰唔想郁定根本唔知咩事 冇人想行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等多幾分鐘 中間開緊會話去北角救人 問大家意見 最後決定咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">北角</span></span>  <br />\n咁冇問題咪去囉 跟住又再傾行路定搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲好多人都大堆物資 搭車唔方便 屌！其實我都唔知點解要行路 大佬都話近唔近呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">算！</span>大家話行咪行囉<br />\n<br />\n好啦到北角 戲肉嚟啦，一到咗冇耐 上面冇人扔野落嚟 唔緊要 屌都見唔到邊間 冇仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再前多少少 就有福建佬嚟打交 姐係你地睇片個個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔夠幾分鐘就完咗比佢地上哂樓 後尾又有d街坊打橫一排叫人唔好追啦 去到呢d位 已經有巴打燥啦 屌9人㩒住佢唔比佢追 話下次你地比人打冇人會幫返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">屌！佢地都敗走哂啦 追可以點追姐 係打就一開波唔好比佢地走咁打啦 人都走哂咁可以點姐</span>唔緊要 平靜過後再行前 去到健威坊個頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌！冇啦啦前面話射咗tg 叫我地退 返去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣</span></span>先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌啦 一嚟cwb on9 二嚟啱啱先到 我想講狗都未見到又話走 咁救乜9人姐 三嚟係轉都唔會返本身既地方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住開始d人都好亂 但一聽到走 就大家唔理唔諗嗌咗轉場先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喂！散風個陣可唔可以用腦諗下先呀？問點解要走又冇乜幾個可以答到 就嗌咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街 一話返去cwb我同班fd都不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on9一陣又話返返北角 彈出彈入好好玩咩 cwb係有野做就做咗啦 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇目的走嚟走去呢d唔係be water 係on橪9咋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後港島區就on99咩都冇做就走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成功一次大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講既係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一</span>，轉場唔係問題 但必須要清楚目標 唔係冇做過野就轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二</span>，咁大班人呢 其實唔適合轉咁多次場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三</span>，大家收到風呢 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好即刻大大聲嗌出嚟</span></span> 好多時都未confirm 需要自己思考下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第四</span>，今次大家唔柒都柒咗 唔好講咩捉鬼又剩啦 當上一堂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次再嚟過 唔好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac6c20b584eb3da472d654d90caa3a17c959f18","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"推比港島橪睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da008cd4e1be3bb8b4859fb4a153992fb0a1c68e","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:29:06.000Z","msg":"推比港島橪睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4537e29f2914f02123ed827d4d3356b23c3f40","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"推比港島橪睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e34f30916d2fda8015c3ef5383a55a728befc2","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"推比港島橪睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7862c925e26a7afb50cbf1e4e995cb818d26485b","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:53:33.000Z","msg":"推比港島橪睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1de4c072339ab3709d6c85e85853e85d5fbb9f1","tid":1419224,"uid":129445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:53:45.00